query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ac.commutative-algebra',
'analytic-number-theory',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'gt.geometric-topology',
'lo.logic',
'matrices',
'nt.number-theory',
'pr.probability',
'ra.rings-and-algebras',
'reference-request',
'rt.representation-theory');
